hopobject.body: Stolen credit card costo de imigran It may seem unusual to come across a bride in black, but then again edgy pop princess Avril Lavigne has never been one to go the conventional route. The 28-year-old singer donned an untraditional, custom-made gown to marry Nickelback frontman Chad Kroeger during an intimate ceremony in the South of France on July 1, 2013. The couple exchanged vows at the Chateau La Napoule in Mandelieu, France in front of family and friends before finishing off the festivities with a lavish dinner and firework display. The couple were engaged in August 2012 after dating six months.
